name: MUI for Figma v5.4.0 (Community)
description:
A free demo of a large UI kit with over 600 handcrafted MUI symbols for Figma.


As of today, this product primarily covers Material UI: the MUI's components that are following the Material Design guidelines.


Click on Duplicate to get your copy.


Get the full version on https://mui.com/store/items/figma-react/. You can report improvement opportunities at https://github.com/mui/mui-design-kits.
